      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To relocate fencing around the Capitol Buildings and the United States Capitol Grounds, and to direct the Secretary of Defense to reassign members of the National Guard deployed to the National Capital Region to the southern land border of the United States.</title>
